Package com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport

Contains classes for communicating schema information with Intelligence Analysis Platform services.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ComplexPropertyValue A generic representation for PropertyValues that contain a list of CompoundPropertyValues
CompoundPropertyValue A generic representation for PropertyValues that contain a list of SimplePropertyValues
DataSource Information about a data source that the Intelligence Analysis Platform connects to.
DataSourceList A container for DataSources.
DateTimePropertyValue A CompoundPropertyValue that represents the current date and time in the locale of the client, and the equivalent date and time in UTC.
DocumentPropertyValue A SimplePropertyValue that represents a binary document in the Analysis Repository.
EntityType An entity type in the Schema.
GeospatialPropertyValue A ComplexPropertyValue that represents a geospatial location.
GradeType One dimension of the grading notation used in the Schema.
ItemType An item type in the Schema.
ItemTypes A container for EntityTypes and LinkTypes within the Schema.
LabelDefinition A description of how the label for a particular ItemType should be generated.
LabelingScheme A container for the LabelDefinitions in the Schema.
LabelPart A description of part of a label, used by a LabelDefinition.
LinkStrength A strength that may be assigned to a Link.
LinkStrengthInfo A container for the LinkStrengths in the Schema.
LinkType A link type in the Schema.
PicturePropertyValue A SimplePropertyValue that represents a picture in the Analysis Repository.
PossibleValue A possible value for a Property with LogicalType.SELECTED_FROM or LogicalType.SUGGESTED_FROM.
ProhibitedCreate A ProhibitedOperation that indicates that users cannot create items, property groups, or properties of a particular type.
ProhibitedEdit A ProhibitedOperation that indicates that users cannot edit existing items, property groups, or properties of a particular type.
ProhibitedOperation An indicator that a user operation is prohibited for items, property groups, or properties of a particular type, as defined in a Schema.
ProhibitedRetrieve A ProhibitedOperation that indicates that users cannot see items, property groups, or properties of a particular type when retrieving data.
PropertyGroupType A property group type in the Schema.
PropertyType A property type in the Schema.
PropertyValue A generic representation for property values that provides the features common to all of them.
Schema A schema in the Intelligence Analysis Platform.
SecurityDimension A dimension for security permissions in the security schema.
SecurityDimensions A container for SecurityDimensions.
SimplePropertyValue A generic representation for PropertyValues that contain exactly one value.
SourceInfoMandatoryFields An indicator of which SourceInfo fields on the Cards of Items whose types are defined in the Schema are mandatory.
 

Enum Summary
DateTimeValidationStatus Indicates whether a supplied date and time value is valid for a particular time zone.
LabelPartType Indicates whether the value of a LabelPart is a string literal, or the identifier of a PropertyType.
LineStyle Indicates how a Link should be rendered.
LogicalType Indicates the data type that a PropertyType in the Schema specifies for its Property values.
PropertyValueType Indicates the type of a PropertyValue, and provides a type-safe way to cast it.
 

Package com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport Description

Contains classes for communicating schema information with Intelligence Analysis Platform services.
